Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:03.80,staffbiaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\frz-90\pos(617,73)}涼宮春日的煩悶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:33.03,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ナゾナゾみたいに地球儀を解き明かしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:36.74,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}みんなでどこまでも行けるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:39.22,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時間の果てまでBoooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:43.54,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ワープでループなこの想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:49.31,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何もかもを巻き込んだ想像で遊ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:52.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}アル晴レタ日ノ事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.67,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}魔法以上のユカイが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:59.98,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}限りなく降りそそぐ　不可能じゃないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:05.83,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日また会うとき　笑いながらハミング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:08.95,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嬉しさを集めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.48,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}カンタンなんだよ　こ{\fe134\fn方正准圆简体\fs23}·{\r}ん{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs23}·{\r}な{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs23}·{\r}の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:16.08,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追いかけてね　つかまえてみて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:20.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大きな夢＆夢　スキでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:33.03,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就像是那地球儀上各種謎團　都一一解說開來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:36.74,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大家就能隨心所欲地到處旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:39.22,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想一直到時間盡頭Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:43.54,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那想法像變成圓圈一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:49.31,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不管什麼都要把這一切捲進幻想裡面去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:52.02,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那晴空之下的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.67,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是比魔法還更加愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:59.98,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永無盡頭地傾注到世界　一切皆有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:05.83,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天再與你見面之時　帶著燦爛笑容輕鬆哼唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:08.95,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}把那些喜悅收集起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.48,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這些其實都非常　簡·單·容·易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:16.08,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}趕快追上去吧　試著抓住它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:20.02,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那雄偉的夢想＆夢想　你喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答えはいつも私の胸に...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:46.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんでだろ　あなたを選んだ私です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:52.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もうとまらない　運命様から決められたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe　真似だけじゃつまらないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:07.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じるまま感じることだけをするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:14.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒険でしょでしょ！ホントが嘘に変わる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:21.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢があるから強くなるのよ　誰の為じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に来てくださいっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:30.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこまでも自由な私を見てよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:35.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日過去になった今日のいまが奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:42.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つかもう未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.27,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份答案一直存在於我的內心裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:46.14,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟為什麼　選擇你的居然會是區區的我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:52.47,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已不能停步　雖然能讓高貴的命運來決定一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.71,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe　單純的模仿一定十分無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.04,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:07.49,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照著感覺走　只去做那感覺到的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:14.34,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒險對吧對吧！在真實變成了謊言的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:21.19,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能夠擁有夢想　就可以收穫堅強　並不是為了誰而去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.56,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請你與我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:30.27,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而看著這個無論何處都會是自由的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:35.66,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天變成過去之前將此日此時的那奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:42.13,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢牢抓住面向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.76,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  朝比奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月份春日建立SOS團之後光陰飛逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經是六月了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在這段時間裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經被捲入了很多將我的世界觀完全推翻的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那些先放在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是這樣一個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！我們要參加棒球大賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:00:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起直到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有發生什麼值得一提的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在享受著悠閒的平靜與無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看來那段日子也只是轉瞬即逝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這傢伙一旦這樣一臉高興地笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼我就會變成疲勞的線操人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說要參加什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九屆室內業餘棒球大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  是誰要去參加這個草地棒球賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（草地棒球：外行人參加的以盡興為目的的棒球比賽）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是我們了！這還用問？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所謂的「我們」是不是把我們幾個也算進去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還需要再找四個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時一樣  是個不把對自己的想法有異議的話聽進耳朵的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂棒球的規則嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我當然知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹我也是嘗試參加過棒球社的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少懂一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然因為一點意思都沒有所以很快就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們為什麼還非要參加\N這種「一點意思都沒有」的棒球大賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是讓全天下知道我們存在的大好機會啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在比賽中獲勝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許SOS團的名號能夠一舉獨步天下呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  是個好主意吧  實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？棒球很不錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先說清楚  我們的目標是最終勝利！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場比賽都不許輸！因為我最討厭失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼乾脆地就答應了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也應該提出一點反駁意見吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起到處亂轉去尋找外星人或者UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（UMA：Unidentified Mysterious Animals，未知生物）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這個活動要健康得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這個比賽什麼時候開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是後天嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說時間也太緊了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經報名了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊伍名稱我已經報好是「SOS團」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡我可是絕不會出錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的四個隊員你打算從哪裡挖啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要隨便逮幾個在那些到處閒晃的人不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真這麼說的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  你先別輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…谷口和國木田好像滿閒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她用「那些」來稱呼同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…還剩下兩個人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…如果我的朋友也可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就也算上那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像什麼人都可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點放心不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼「時候」  什麼「地方」交的朋友啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在這個時間…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在班上認識的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也來推薦一個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上  我認識的一個人對我們的事很感興趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的人選由我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然決定好了就馬上來特訓吧！特訓！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓？現在就開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我們就要去參加棒球比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個答案很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是  只不過是因為春日她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點煩悶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個地方借給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有棒球用具也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們必須要趕快進行棒球訓練嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們比較礙事  閃開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼可能答應啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛！只借一陣子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是容易被看穿的青春時期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼先打個一千棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這球上可寄託了SOS團的未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我好好接住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次聽說我們的未來原來是寄託在這麼小的一個球上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  要來了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還站得起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和我感情這麼好的話  又會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！阿虛！實玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們受傷退場！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面棒球社的給我補上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人吃驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的正好是打了一千棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是連這個都能數得一清二楚的你比較令我吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  長門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽當天能不能讓老天下場雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是能讓比賽中止的那種大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對局部性的環境資料進行篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有對行星生態系統造成後遺症的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後遺症是…大約多久以後會發作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾百年到一萬年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是別這麼做比較好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  比賽當天來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…其實不來臨也沒什麼問題的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是阿虛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常聽實玖瑠提起你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這位是我的朋友鶴屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谷口  請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是國木田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～阿虛是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的請求我實在沒辦法拒絕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是谷口和國木田對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這是我們的光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙你也想讓她上場打球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「那種傢伙」也太失禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說可也是我的妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自我介紹說是「小學五年級生  現在十歲」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個坦率到無法聯想到是你妹妹一般的好孩子呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過重點在於我們參加的可是一般年齡層的棒球賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是青少年級的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊春日小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會把妹妹帶來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說本來就不可能打贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這可是春日搞出來的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一不小心真的最終勝出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會變成超級麻煩的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果混一個小學五年級生進去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣能贏才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好稍微放一下水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果贏得太狠也就太不給對手面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像她還真的想要打贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有決定打擊順序和守備位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個來決定！沒有意見了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有打擊的順序和防守的位置兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我是投手和一棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想好的只有決定的方法嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼  你有什麼不滿意的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是民主的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古希臘可是還用抽籤來選政治家呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把古希臘的政治制度\N和現代日本的草地棒球打擊順序混為一談好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只有你可以按照興趣來選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼民主啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字      守備位置\N一棒  涼宮春日  投手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二棒  實玖瑠    右外野\N三棒  有希      中間手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:58.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四棒  阿虛      二壘手\N五棒  虛妹      左外野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六棒  古泉      捕手\N七棒  國木田    一壘手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八棒  鶴屋      三壘手\N九棒  谷口      游擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來能夠更快地回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛剛聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一場的對手是叫做「上上原海盜」的大學生球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本屆大賽的種子隊伍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只要得分相差10分就會提前結束比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就開始準備回家應該也不算早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Play Ball！{\r}\N比賽開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他投的球完全沒什麼好怕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都跟上來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這廝對著朝比奈學姐投得是什麼該死的球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我打到她身上一個看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去跟你們群毆！把這裡變成群毆狂歡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使勁打啊！使勁！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！為什麼不揮棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希！如果不揮棒的話不是就更不會打中了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  你一定要打中啊！你可是四棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一般四棒的位置會安排打擊力最強的隊員，稱之為強打或強棒）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在期待我這個抽籤決定的四棒做些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日是面對這種球打出長打的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡！你在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴防死守吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Play！{\r}\N比賽繼續！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊刃有餘啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Foul ball！{\r}\N界外球！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她只會衝著好球區投直球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被人看出來當然會被打中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們守備的漏洞比熱帶大草原上蟻巢的還要多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹筐一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一回合總算是把失分控制在2分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為對方的勝利女神來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天誰都希望休息一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  第二輪的攻勢也是毫無懸念地結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:39.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:40.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後又很乾脆地被對方拿下了幾分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來下一回合就可以結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Out！{\r}\N出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難了吧  光是讓球棒打到球就用盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是需要那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　Time{\r}\N先暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮同學…不  不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！快點給我脫好換衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  可以拍下來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是綁個馬尾比較好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  來加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  要怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼做～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  大聲加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各  各位！請打中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你們了  加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的～包在我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種球果然還是打不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正也沒指望你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上壘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠！這次一定要打中哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:05.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}上吧！實玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:05.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝比奈學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠！這個啊  用這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這樣能讓對方投手的MP減少嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像是在打暗號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們決定過什麼暗號嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想那大概是叫她用搶分戰術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（搶分戰術：跑者在三壘時，打擊手使用犧牲打令跑者得以回本壘的戰術）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人出局還打搶分戰術的暗號？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那個永世教練也會用更常識性的戰術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:36.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（永世教練：指巨人隊的長島教練，\N巨人隊時代教練都由長島家的人擔任而得名。被很多球迷厭惡）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是發現了朝比奈打中球的幾率基本上是零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是因此做出意義不明的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意讓對方看透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會令內野手出現失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是希望朝比奈同學用犧牲打打中球的話也能有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然完全被人家看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:14:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  你給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後咬緊牙關！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是懲罰  懲罰！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓大家看看你這張可笑的臉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打出莫名其妙暗號的你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去盜本壘不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不想聽  不過你姑且說說看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個前所未有的大規模封閉空間開始產生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還正在以非常快的速度擴大著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要涼宮同學的心情不恢復  它就會持續擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那個」也就會繼續大肆破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為打輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不懂事的小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你說得好像是別人的事情一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這和你也有很大的關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為決定打擊順序的時候我們不是抽籤了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而作為結果  你是四棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不覺得高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為涼宮同學這樣希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才成為了第四棒打擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  你完全沒有起到四棒的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這一回合盡全力令比賽不要提前結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在比賽結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等同於世界末日來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！要開始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  都要把失分控制在兩分以內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人出局  跑者在一  二壘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在零對九
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一分就會強制結束比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕上啊  要趕上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice Play！幹得不錯嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的好友！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續剛才的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉湊得太近了  什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次和涼宮同學一起到那個世界去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼回來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我想起那件事來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用那一招的話  也許又能夠順利解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就用些能夠確保勝利的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和她之間的利害關係應該也是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門同學終於也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像在詠唱咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文？那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這是禁止談論的事項
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:18:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊！你怎麼有這麼大的力氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  對屬性資訊作了能力提升改寫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制導模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛得好遠！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  制導模式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  亂來也要有點限度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  再這樣下去就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各種意義上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才忘記說了  第一場比賽時間限制為90分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以已經沒有下一回合了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要守住這一回合  我們就獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？就這樣獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不獲勝不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧如此  封閉空間的擴大速度似乎已經降下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果在這裡被對方逆轉局勢的話可就再見滑鐵盧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過猜那個時候春日心情如何也沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我有個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常當真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把這一回合的失分控制在最低
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這個方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Ball！{\r}\N壞球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你給我好好投！難得我和你交換位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果輸了的話就罰你請所有人吃飯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  我投的球可是負擔著全世界的命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這個世界還真是不值錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於這Mysterious Ball（命名：我）的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來世界不需要被毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}S…Strike two！{\r}\N兩…兩好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的打擊手也很無聊地被三球三振了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕會已經成為最後的打擊手的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也已經兩好球了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike two！{\r}\N兩好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  還有一球  決出勝負吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不說這球也會決定勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  上上原海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僥倖！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不死三振了！長門！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不死三振：在一壘無人情況下，\N捕手未能接到應該能將打擊手三振的球時，打擊手安全衝上一壘）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去撿起球來投過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二壘！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這一群人稍微有點超乎常理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Ga…game and set！{\r}\N比…比賽結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:30.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日文的省略讀法讀作「Game set」）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然由於長門的作弊式魔法我們打贏了這一場…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二場要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就這樣繼續打第二場的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些對不起上上原海盜  而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也差不多該去給「同伴」們幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話人數也不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棄權吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不能讓涼宮同學閒下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就作為今後的課題吧  有研究的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也玩夠了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉說有急事要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腿和手臂也都累得動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你覺得可以  那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有些餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃午飯吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太感謝你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你這根球棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都沒有注意到過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來我有打棒球的天分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是長門有希？聽實玖瑠她經常提到你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家盡量多吃點吧  今天阿虛請客～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我口袋裡也有一筆臨時收入了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我衷心期盼上上原海盜隊能拿下傲人戰績
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐生！好好打！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來遲啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這次參加哪個好？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球和美式橄欖球都是多少人參加的運動？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用之前的那些人夠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一面看著春日最美麗的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始考慮哪個是人數最少的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美式橄欖球…不！去給我打門球吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:18.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一種只需要5個人的球類運動）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:15.93,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[三種不同的茶杯…這個細節我都不記得了OTL]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:43.74,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[不帶眼鏡的長門大明神啊～！（大心）]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:50.18,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「…而現在那套女僕裝已經用衣架掛起來，吊在社團活動室的角落了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.50,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「因為沒有人有任何反應，所以一如往常還是由我勉為其難地反問春日。\N為什麼大家老是把我當成和春日溝通的管道？\N再沒有任何事情比這個任務更讓我傷腦筋的了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.37,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「主辦單位是市公所，似乎是歷史悠久、每年都會舉辦的活動」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:29.88,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「我全身一陣虛脫」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:45.42,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「而且春日會鎖定的人除了一個例外，向來都不是普通人。\N那個極少數的例外就是我。而我並不打算再認識更多來歷不明的人了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.40,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[（春日：）「總比沒有好」]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.06,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[這裡特別配合台版小說翻譯成「煩悶」…不過其實還是無聊比較準確OTL]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:39.05,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「你好歹也多動一點吧。還是我該誇獎你動態視力極佳呢？」]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.85,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「…一個不規則彈跳的硬球掠過我的手套，\N穿過我的胯下，直接命中了朝比奈的膝蓋。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.09,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「又會怎樣？我聳聳肩。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.64,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「好久遠的未來啊」]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.27,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[等過了暑假保准你不會再這麼說。]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.50,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[通稱：虛妹]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.82,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[上上原海盜是台版小說的翻譯，\N原文「上ヶ原パイレーツ」，感覺譯作「上原海盜」就可以了…]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.41,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「春日氣勢洶洶地大叫。可是，她這種做法完全是反效果。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.21,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「因為這麼一來，對方選手對女生手下留情的心情早就消失得無影無蹤了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.87,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[原文「亂闘パーティー」…難道是在EG「亂○派對」？！]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.67,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「…事實上，我感覺投手投出球的那一刹那，球就已經進入捕手的手套裡了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.84,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「哇！球轉彎了。這就是所謂的曲球嗎？」]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.35,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「春日帶著彷彿被伊阿宋背叛的美狄亞公主般的眼神，\N看著在內也跑了一圈的對方第三棒打擊手」\N（和動畫略有不同）]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.50,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「（春日）發現我投注過去的視線之後，\N她把嘴巴嘟得像鴨子一樣尖，放棄弄頭髮了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.30,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「腦」]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.08,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「古泉帶著與充滿危機感的說話內容完全不搭調的表情說著」]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:16.28,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[苦啊！苦啊！]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:47.72,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「SELECT serial code FROM database WHERE code data ORDER BY 攻擊性資訊戰鬥 HAVING terminate mode。\Npersonal name 朝倉涼子，判斷為敵性。\N解除該對象的有機資訊連結。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:48.77,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[按原文看來貌似長門是在對某「主機」下達指令，\N（如上我所寫的）大寫的部分是命令格式，小寫和中文部分是具體參數吧…]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.62,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「…因為我覺得對方選手的視線不在我們這些選手身上，\N反倒全集中在這支球棒上了。…」]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.75,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[搞不好對方也打算開群毆派對…？]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:16.58,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[這個BGM明顯是在惡搞Touch的同名第一期OP…]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:39.34,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[中文讀作：由於這神秘魔球括弧命名我的緣故]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:51.05,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[這個時候對方應該學春日跳詛咒之舞削減阿虛（其實是長門…）的MP了…]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.71,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[MP不足！]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.08,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「長門以釐米為單位，微微地對我點點頭——」——沒有表現出來！…吧？]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.32,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[（虛：）「別把我概括在你們這些超乎常理的人當中啊」]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.89,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[研究的成果就是女僕和管家…]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:12.53,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[其實是「從異空間脫出用的那一招」的輕量版…\N總之就是阿虛給涼宮殺必死就對了。]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:44.39,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[看來是訛了一筆…]


